description:
Job Responsibilities:

Responsible for the detailed design of vehicle power supply application software, including MBD model design, Unit Test, integration test;

Responsible for OBC and DCDC vehicle matching verification and problem solving.

Responsible for software development process quality activities and doc writing

Job requirements:

More than 3 years of embedded software development experience;

Understand the vehicle development and verification process;

Familiar with C language and MISRA-C standard;

Experience in MBD model development is preferred;

Experience in automotive power supply design is preferred.
